{
  "stem": "8212.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It wasn't just one show, when you showed couture.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It-- you showed through two months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You showed the press, and you showed private customers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But you had a show every single day with models.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I just helped in all kinds of capacities-- writing, seating people, whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was part of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was extraordinary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The good part about it was, also, that the mother of Monsieur [INAUDIBLE] was a fashion editor at a big magazine called And he introduced me to her, and after a few months of [?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Maggie Wolf, ?] I started freelancing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I got jobs through the magazine to go to different houses and just make fashion sketches, which they published there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Also, during that time, I went to sketch to an academy to learn how to sketch nudes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there I met a wonderful person, who was Viennese like me and who had gone to America and come back to France and wanted to do the same thing as I did, fashion illustration and fashion creation.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the two of us got together, and she had a much nicer room than I, because she had come back from America and she had more means.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She also had much nicer clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what we did is we sketched each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We made a whole portfolio of marvelous fashion sketches, she of me and I of her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, I was very small, so was she, so we added the proportions of a fashion model.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used her furs, her scarves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We sat.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We made poses.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we made a whole portfolio.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we both had D Day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went out to show it to magazines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we both were accepted in magazines.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
